  <thing id="ra5CSavFac" name="Saving Face" description="If you miss with an attack roll or fail an ability check or a saving throw, you can gain a bonus to the roll equal to the number of allies you can see within 30 feet of you (maximum bonus of +5). Once you use this trait, you can&apos;t use it again until you finish a short or long rest." compset="RaceSpec">
