  <thing id="ma5CShFarS" name="Shield of Far Sight" description="This shield allows the mind flayer that created it the ability to view through the eye mounted on the shield. As long as it is on the same plane of existence as the mind flayer, the mind flayer can see through the eye, which has darkvision out to 60 feet. While peering through the eye, the mind flayer can use its Mind Blast action as though it were standing behind the shield.\n\nIf the shield of far sight is destroyed, the mind flayer that created it is blinded for 2d12 hours." compset="MagicArmor">
