  <thing id="ma5CSurMan" name="Survival Mantle" description="This carapace crafted by mind flayers encases parts of the wearer&apos;s shoulders, neck, and chest, functioning like a suit of half plate. While wearing it, the creature can breath normally in any environment (including vacuum) and has advantage on saving throws against harmful gases." compset="MagicArmor">
